Package de.elo.ix.client

Class SordType

java.lang.Object
byps.BValueClass
de.elo.ix.client.ValueClass
de.elo.ix.client.SordType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SordType
extends ValueClass
implements java.io.Serializable
Each file structure element is assigned a SordType. This SordType has three icons , which are used in the different view in the client: a standard icon, a disabled icon (empty folders or references) and a workflow icon.
The icons are available in BMP, ICO and JPEG format.
